   MaxLd = MAX(0,P/2-M/L3)                                           =      7.95 kN/mm
   A < L1
   Tension per bolt, Ten=(fp*A*B/2-P)/Nrow/2                         =     29.60 kN
   a, distance from flange to edge of plate                          =     157.3 mm
   A >= a, therefore M=fp*(a^2/2-a^3/6/A)                            =      1.73 kN-m
   a2, distance from flange to nearest bolt + 0.025*d                =      82.3 mm
   perf, percentage of force to flange = (G/2)^3/ ((G/2)^3+(a2)^3)   =      0.18
   gwid, flange gusset width = (pltlen-d)/2                          =     147.0 mm
   Bolt head dia, HeadDia                                            =      33.0 mm
   xbar1 = distance from center of flange to farthest bolt           =       0.0 mm
   Percentage of force to flange, Perf=(G/2)^3/(xbar1^3 + (G/2)^3)   =      0.00 mm
   xbar=xbar1-headdia/2-(flgthk)/2                                   =      55.5 mm
   ybar=G/2-Headdia-(Flg gusset thick)/2                             =      28.5 mm
   M1=Perf*Ten*xbar/(MIN(HeadDia+2*xbar , B/2-(flg gusset thick)/2)) =    0.1004 kN-m
